data.actual_result: The audio is very static and robotic
data.expected_result: There should be no static audio
data.short_description: When being in a voice chat then start a game with the overlay enabled, the voice chat gets very static after a few seconds
data.steps_to_repro: - Join a voice channel with someone - Enable the overlay - Launch a game - Wait until you see "Discord overlay blabla, keybind" popup inside the game - Observe how the voice chat gets very very static after a few seconds
